sys_hub_flow.description:
Retrieves entire data or updates made after the last refresh, for the selected entities.

  • Set 'Retrieve All Data' to 'True' to retrieve entire data of the selected entities.
  • If 'Retrieve All Data' is set to 'False', only the updates made after the last refresh are retrieved.
  • If data hasn’t been retrieved for the selected entity, entire data is retrieved irrespective of the value provided for 'Retrieve All Data'.

Inputs:

  • Department - Retrieves the department data from Workday.
  • Location - Retrieves the location data from Workday.
  • Job Profile - Retrieves the job profile data from Workday.
  • Worker Profile - Retrieves the worker profile data from Workday.
  • Effective Worker Profile - Retrieves the Effective Worker Profiles data from Workday.
  • Future Worker Profile - Retrieves the Future Worker Profiles data from Workday.
  • Employment Data - Retrieves the Employment data from Workday.
  • Retrieve All Data - Retrieves entire data for the selected entities.

To use this subflow, Workday Spoke must be installed and corresponding Workday Connection and Credential must be created.

sys_hub_flow_snapshot.description:
Retrieves entire data or updates made after the last refresh, for the selected entities.

  • Set 'Retrieve All Data' to 'True' to retrieve entire data of the selected entities.
  • If 'Retrieve All Data' is set to 'False', only the updates made after the last refresh are retrieved.
  • If data hasn’t been retrieved for the selected entity, entire data is retrieved irrespective of the value provided for 'Retrieve All Data'.

Inputs:

  • Department - Retrieves the department data from Workday.
  • Location - Retrieves the location data from Workday.
  • Job Profile - Retrieves the job profile data from Workday.
  • Worker Profile - Retrieves the worker profile data from Workday.
  • Effective Worker Profile - Retrieves the Effective Worker Profiles data from Workday.
  • Future Worker Profile - Retrieves the Future Worker Profiles data from Workday.
  • Employment Data - Retrieves the Employment data from Workday.
  • Retrieve All Data - Retrieves entire data for the selected entities.

To use this subflow, Workday Spoke must be installed and corresponding Workday Connection and Credential must be created.

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_hub_flow"><sys_hub_flow action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><acls/><active>true</active><annotation/><callable_by_client_api>false</callable_by_client_api><category/><copied_from>7d0f03b11b92545067817669cc4bcb80</copied_from><copied_from_name>Run Workday Service</copied_from_name><description>
<p>Retrieves entire data or updates made after the last refresh, for the selected entities.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Set 'Retrieve All Data' to 'True' to retrieve entire data of the selected entities.</li>
    <li>If 'Retrieve All Data' is set to 'False', only the updates made after the last refresh are retrieved.</li>
    <li>If data hasn’t been retrieved for the selected entity, entire data is retrieved irrespective of the value provided for 'Retrieve All Data'.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Inputs:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Department</strong> - Retrieves the department data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Location</strong> - Retrieves the location data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Job Profile</strong> - Retrieves the job profile data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the worker profile data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Effective Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the Effective Worker Profiles data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Future Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the Future Worker Profiles data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Employment Data</strong> - Retrieves the Employment data  from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Retrieve All Data</strong> - Retrieves entire data for the selected entities.</li>
</ul>
<p>To use this subflow, Workday Spoke must be installed and corresponding Workday Connection and Credential must be <p>Retrieves entire data or updates made after the last refresh, for the selected entities.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Set 'Retrieve All Data' to 'True' to retrieve entire data of the selected entities.</li>
    <li>If 'Retrieve All Data' is set to 'False', only the updates made after the last refresh are retrieved.</li>
    <li>If data hasn’t been retrieved for the selected entity, entire data is retrieved irrespective of the value provided for 'Retrieve All Data'.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Inputs:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Department</strong> - Retrieves the department data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Location</strong> - Retrieves the location data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Job Profile</strong> - Retrieves the job profile data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the worker profile data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Effective Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the Effective Worker Profiles data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Future Worker Profile</strong> - Retrieves the Future Worker Profiles data from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Employment Data</strong> - Retrieves the Employment data  from Workday.</li>
    <li><strong>Retrieve All Data</strong> - Retrieves entire data for the selected entities.</li>
</ul>
